  "summary": "Malicious code in gptcore (npm)",
  "details": "The package gptcore@4.0.6 runs a remote code downloader during npm install. The preinstall script (package/preinstall.js) executes mshta.exe to fetch and run an HTA payload from hxxp://fixars[.]top. The main module (gptcore.js) is a decoy LLM API client with no relation to the malicious behaviour. The IOC is the remote host fixars[.]top accessed via mshta on Windows systems.",
